@startuml
Actor User as user
Boundary System as system
Database data.txt as file

user -> system: Analyze data
system -> file: Read data from file
system -> user: Request data type
user -> system: Select data type
system -> user: Ask for filters (hourly/daily/weekly/monthly)
system -> system: Filter data
system -> system: Analyze data
system --> user: Display analyze result
@enduml